{"type": "article", "id": 62512, "title": "RIMOWA和B&O合作联名款耳机，Facebook 因歧视广告被起诉 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人的一切", "date": "2019-03-29T05:00:08Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 413, "name": "耳机"}, {"id": 6544, "name": "种族歧视"}, {"id": 16699, "name": "RIMOWA"}, {"id": 13583, "name": "三只松鼠"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 1480589, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 23, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190329125536AruID6Li7F8fXb0O.jpg", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">明星又代言了啥</h3><p line=\"h9Pl\" class=\"\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4355119241709315?\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\" rel=\"nofollow\">膳魔师宣布朱一龙成为品牌代言人。</a>之前他已经是 Young 系列产品代言人。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329131140lksA2fGvIEdLqpMc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.778704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"h9Pl\"><b><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4354756733008729?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">林更新成为膜法世家代言人，</a></b>之前还有吴磊、薛之谦和周冬雨。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329125642lTEs14aejhXGUSDV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.597667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>又是跨界</h3><p line=\"Xmek\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4354877771488824?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>RIMOWA 和 Bang &amp; Olufsen 推出联名耳机 Beoplay H9i。</b></a>这款头戴式无线蓝牙耳机选择阳极化铝材质，收纳盒也是 RIMOWA 经典旅行箱造型。</p><p line=\"Xmek\">目前已经确定将于 4 月 15 日在北京 SKP、上海恒隆广场、上海国金中心商场、深圳万象城和广州太古汇 RIMOWA 精品店发售。此外，RIMOWA 微信线上店， B&amp;O 天猫、京东和微信线上官方旗舰店都会同步售卖。价格为 6998 元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329125703CGhNbAJrR5TeKszt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329125703tUK5J0SRjaAMgEmo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201903291257041L5bBCsINMjU2YrZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329125704vYMnD7tOeChlPzUQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329125704BJ46Cl0y8M53fDTN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>值得一看的 Case</h3><p line=\"bArx\" class=\"\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5ODMyODUwMA==&amp;mid=2651491828&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=9efd27e3894bf04340378c477bf2c920&amp;chksm=bd324c2f8a45c53989e6e70b95bbbd218670e9734ef762605a60328dccc2f4d7f7739b76a9cf&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=0329McJP5LQMyMOwzF49DswF&amp;key=f1b1b4aaf75e0cb51f35b54c25ff283a45982147ce943deda73b891014396294e1d4fb0fef07e0cf862c142205a8f6457b550d12385d66920c1162639fc297d53c6b06815cc8ed90da02cd6d186be553&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MjgzNjA1MjcyMQ%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir7%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.14.3+build(18D109)&amp;version=12020010&amp;nettype=WIFI&amp;lang=en&amp;fontScale=100&amp;pass_ticket=%2F%2Ff96zLx9CSpx3Xp%2F5IAEn6oYBQWNNLWdYNDlPrXqwIWbZrI1%2Bw5efWcGxQLgs11\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>盛大游戏更名为盛趣游戏，还换了个新 Logo。</b></a>将原先传统的红橙色调变为红蓝绿橙四色，更加平面化。盛趣游戏的解释是，红蓝绿橙分别代表传承、科技、健康和活力，开口则是为了表示企业未来更加开放。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329125755hZw1QuxeGl3F6gic.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.909348\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"bArx\" class=\"\"><b><a href=\"https://youtu.be/mjLuy5U9PNU\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">拉斯维加斯的棕榈树赌场度假酒店（Palms Casino Resort）拍了个浮华的广告片。</a></b>片中找来 Cardi B 、Rita Ora 和 Emily Ratajkowski 等明星出演，并聚集了 Damien Hirst 和 Andy Warhol 的艺术品。整体风格浮夸又纵意，这是酒店品牌活动 “Unstatus Quo” 的一部分。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=c0855bvb0vm\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"Kxdw\" class=\"\"><a href=\"https://youtu.be/c5V28rn-9S8\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>科罗娜用一分钟广告片回顾了品牌历史。</b></a>片中场景是由导演 Menard 和 Nexus 工作室合作制作，每一段重要故事都像舞台剧开启下一幕。创意代理商是 Observatory Marketing。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=d0855dh7cza\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"gkPQ\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/2559971200/4354893470656177\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>三只松鼠推出 “53” 零食大礼包，</b></a>这次是“5 年防骗，3 年补脑”。里面包括 5 袋坚果零食，礼包是愚人节限定，总共 1000 份。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201903291259319VcXE0L1K8WfiUBy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329125931x1Tky0RPfSX9WwLm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329125932TduLKQ2rAgwpxDnG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.777778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"JC42\">它还和网易新闻推出 H5 <b><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA5Mjk4MzU2MA==&amp;mid=2650818373&amp;idx=3&amp;sn=fcdeb4761d00381c9c3a0d62fb0fa341&amp;chksm=8b903f22bce7b634dfb729f898034ad6ba7371f51ca4c951981ff9f0a994ce254aeb44b67b08&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=0329x2Ly0rLtDipVcFitojju&amp;key=e26fe09897582c58bb7c36c8bb52b8701810c2954b4b534b3c0c63aa8e9e308354e866145d1d2159a8b38258ab31a7ce9d3362530f72cac8e94c250d3603c9a41b7b45593971148e61478cc49e3ce0aa&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MjgzNjA1MjcyMQ%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir7%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.14.3+build(18D109)&amp;version=12020010&amp;nettype=WIFI&amp;lang=en&amp;fontScale=100&amp;pass_ticket=%2F%2Ff96zLx9CSpx3Xp%2F5IAEn6oYBQWNNLWdYNDlPrXqwIWbZrI1%2Bw5efWcGxQLgs11\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">“全国防骗模拟考试”</a>，</b>脑力值用光，广告就出现了，答案并不重要。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329125947NuF1bzETRK3JWvoC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.931250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329125958jV4BcHvUdAnZ5FSP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.482667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329125958tBT3vj9VgzeXkKaZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.485333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"L1il\"><a href=\"https://lbbonline.com/news/these-galaxy-ads-are-accidentally-renaissance-on-purpose/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>德芙将巧克力装裱进画框之中。</b></a>荷兰摄影师 Gemmy Woud-Binnendijk 为品牌拍摄了一系列现代生活享受巧克力的瞬间，但运用了文艺复兴时期作品的华丽风格，创意代理商是 BBDO /都柏林.</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201903291300215R2Q8PhA01XjYVib.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329130020flXEuoPwKv6U0pM9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.501176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190329130020zHIGvRd5eohZBCiA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>其他，也很重要</h3><p line=\"tWqA\"><a href=\"https://www.theverge.com/2019/3/28/18285178/facebook-hud-lawsuit-fair-housing-discrimination\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>美国政府起诉了 Facebook 的歧视性住房广告。</b></a>美国住房和城市发展部表示 Facebook 违反了《公平住房法》，它的广告定位系统允许房东根据种族和居住地来限制广告受众。</p><p line=\"5Voc\">2016 年新媒体 ProPublica 的记者首次发现，系统的特定广告会排除黑人或者西班牙裔用户。当时没有明确特定广告是住房或是就业机会。</p><p line=\"LlAJ\">Facebook 去年 8 月删除了 5000 个特定的定位选项，包括取消特定种族和宗教。最近，它又取消了按照年龄、性别或者邮政编码来定位住房广告，以此争取和各种民权组织和解。</p><p line=\"tFAg\">这是第一起针对定向广告中的种族歧视提起的诉讼。</p><p line=\"fgeA\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3ODgwNTAzNw==&amp;mid=2659023854&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=bc44d0b5c04aac65e7c28c71f322cac3&amp;chksm=8434faacb34373ba438835b39befa238087c0db99b6d77480fbfa32f3b32bf6d4291dd4dfc9f&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=&amp;key=90cb886f1cc7938c1ef97fd7d3f591a8f14648e3fdd5b67b7ff32ae4d72da78f39c9079910153e3102305e618adc9707984cc4af86166694fa268086f2b6c340a70c886854a31b2a7049b9788fdfddb8&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MjgzNjA1MjcyMQ%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir7%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.14.3+build(18D109)&amp;version=12020010&amp;nettype=WIFI&amp;lang=en&amp;fontScale=100&amp;pass_ticket=%2F%2Ff96zLx9CSpx3Xp%2F5IAEn6oYBQWNNLWdYNDlPrXqwIWbZrI1%2Bw5efWcGxQLgs11\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>“微信广告助手”官方小程序上线。</b></a>广告主和服装商的运营人员可以在移动端查看账户数据，包括投放计划和广告核心数据；管理广告，包含暂停和启动广告，修改预算和出价，查看审核结果等功能。</p><p line=\"fgeA\" class=\"\">题图来自：RIMOWA </p>"}